#, no-wrap
msgid "`desthack`"
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block = 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/uses/_index.adoc:319
msgid ""
"Changes the behavior of GNU configure to properly support `DESTDIR` in case "
"the original software does not."
msgstr ""

