#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/porters-handbook/uses/_index.adoc:1129
msgid ""
"Possible arguments: (none), `phpize`, `ext`, `zend`, `build`, `cli`, `cgi`, "
"`mod`, `web`, `embed`, `pecl`, `flavors`, `noflavors`"
